<title>JESUH ZUMH CU A NUAM CH296</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh zumh cu a tha bik ko, A bia bang in zumh a nuam, A biakam
 chungah i dinh le hngalh cu, Bawipa nih a duh.

[C1]
   Jesuh, Jesuh, ka zumhning cu, Lungtak in ka ruat than tawn, Jesuh,
   Jesuh, mi sung Jesuh, A vel ruangah ka zumh chin.

[V2]
 Jesuh zumh cu a tha hringhran, A thi in a ka tawlnak, Damnak ti thiang
 ah a ka hnim, Ka zumhnak a tlawm na-in.

[C2]
   Jesuh, Jesuh, ka zumhning cu, Lungtak in ka ruat than tawn, Jesuh,
   Jesuh, mi sung Jesuh, A vel ruangah ka zumh chin.

[V3]
 Jesuh zumh cu a tha taktak, Sual lung-puamnak cu a hloh, Jesuh nih a
 dawtnak ruangah, Zungzal a ka umpi lai.

[C3]
   Jesuh, Jesuh, ka zumhning cu, Lungtak in ka ruat than tawn, Jesuh,
   Jesuh, mi sung Jesuh, A vel ruangah ka zumh chin.

[V4]
 Ka zumh ca ka lung a lawm khun, Misung Jesuh hawitha bik, Ka sinah a
 um ti ka hngalh, Zungzal a ka umpi lai.

[C4]
   Jesuh, Jesuh, ka zumhning cu, Lungtak in ka ruat than tawn, Jesuh,
   Jesuh, mi sung Jesuh, A vel ruangah ka zumh chin.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
</song>